---
source: crates/franken-node/tests/cli_subcommand_goldens.rs
---
Fleet control plane operations

Usage: franken-node fleet <COMMAND>

Commands:
  status     Show policy and quarantine state across nodes
  release    Lift quarantine[PATH] controls with receipts
  reconcile  Reconcile fleet state for convergence
  agent      Run as a fleet agent that polls for and applies fleet actions
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
